"title": "6684: mediator",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6684: mediator",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>An intermediary who intervenes betwen two separated or alienated parties, with the aim of achieving reconciliation and fellowship. Scripture declares that Jesus Christ is the only true mediator between God and humanity.</p>\n<h2>A person who brings together those who are separated from each other</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:14\">2SA 14:14</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Mediators between God and humanity before the time of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Abraham</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:22-Gen18:32\">GEN 18:22–18:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:7\">GEN 20:7</a></p>\n<h3>Moses</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:5\">DEU 5:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:30-Exod32:32\">EXO 32:30–32:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:27\">DEU 5:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:18\">DEU 9:18</a></p>\n<h3>Prophets</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut18:18\">DEU 18:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:15\">2CH 36:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:25\">JER 7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:7\">AMO 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:34\">MAT 23:34</a></p>\n<h3>Priests</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num3:10\">NUM 3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:6\">EXO 19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev9:7\">LEV 9:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:48\">NUM 16:48</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num18:7\">NUM 18:7</a></p>\n<h3>The suffering servant</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:6\">ISA 49:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:1\">ISA 42:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:4\">ISA 42:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:4-Isa53:6\">ISA 53:4–53:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:10-Isa53:12\">ISA 53:10–53:12</a></p>\n<h3>Angels</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:53\">ACT 7:53</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:1\">JOB 5:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job16:19-Job16:21\">JOB 16:19–16:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:23\">JOB 33:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:13\">DAN 4:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:23\">DAN 4:23</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ is the only true mediator</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:5\">1TI 2:5</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ as greater than all OT mediators</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:17\">JHN 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:1-Heb3:6\">HEB 3:1–3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:26-Heb7:28\">HEB 7:26–7:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb8:6\">HEB 8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:23-Heb9:24\">HEB 9:23–9:24</a></p>\n<h2>Mediators between people</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:1-2Sam14:33\">2SA 14:1–14:33</a> <em>Joab</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:9\">MAT 5:9</a> <em>Christians</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:26-Acts9:27\">ACT 9:26–9:27</a> <em>Barnabas</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:10-1Cor1:12\">1CO 1:10–1:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:2-Phil4:3\">PHP 4:2–4:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:17-Phlm1:21\">PHM 1:17–1:21</a></p>",
